snippet.title: Mowgli Teaser | Roshan Kanakala | Sandeep Raj | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad | PMF
snippet.description:
Mowgli is an upcoming unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Cast: Roshan Kanakala, Sakkshi Mhadolkar, Bandi Saroj Kumar & Harsha Chemudu

Technical Crew:
Writer & Director: Sandeep Raj
Producers: TG Vishwa Prasad, Krithi Prasad
Banner: People Media Factory
Music: Kaala Bhairava

snippet.title: 12A Railway Colony - Trailer | Allari Naresh | Kamakshi Bhaskarla | Bheems Ceciroleo | Nani
snippet.description:
The thrilling theatrical trailer of ‚Äú12A Railway Colony‚Äù is finally out, and it promises an intense cinematic experience packed with suspense, mystery, and unexpected twists. Directed and edited by Nani Kasaragadda and written by Dr. Anil Viswanath, the creative mind behind Polimera and Polimera 2, the film takes viewers on a gripping journey through secrets hidden in the shadows of a quiet railway colony. Backed by Srinivasaa Silver Screen and produced by Srinivasaa Chitturi, with Pavan Kumar presenting, the film‚Äôs visuals and edge-of-the-seat narrative are already generating buzz among thriller lovers.

snippet.title: The Devil Wears Prada 2 | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A sequel? For spring? Groundbreaking. Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt, and Stanley Tucci return in The Devil Wears Prada 2, in theaters May 1, 2026. Watch the teaser trailer now.¬†

Almost twenty years after making their iconic turns as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigel‚ÄîMeryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation. 
 
The film reunites the original main cast with director David Frankel and writer Aline Brosh McKenna, and introduces an all-new runway of characters including Kenneth Branagh, Simone Ashley, Justin Theroux, Lucy Liu, Patrick Brammall, Caleb Hearon, Helen J. Shen, Pauline Chalamet, B.J. Novak and Conrad Ricamora. Tracie Thoms and Tibor Feldman also reprise their roles as ‚ÄúLily‚Äù and ‚ÄúIrv‚Äù from the first film. 
 
‚ÄúThe Devil Wears Prada 2‚Äù is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1, 2026.

snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. With a penthouse to protect and a baby to burp, will Trevor be able to have the calm Christmas he hopes for, or will festivities descend into chaos?

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81516058

snippet.description:
Welcome to the World of Vrusshabha.

A unique story brought to life through an unforgettable cinematic experience for global audiences. With Mohanlal playing a king for the very first time in a bilingual epic, Vrusshabha is a film that promises to stay with you long after you leave the theatre. Vrusshabha is a grand Pan Indian film shot simultaneously in Malayalam and Telugu, and dubbed in Hindi and Kannada.

snippet.title: Easily 3 Star the Last Town Hall 17 Challenge (Clash of Clans)
snippet.description:
How to 3 Star the Last TH17 Challenge in Clash of Clans. Judo Sloth provides a tutorial for the new event attack which showcases the 3 Star by Cronos of Tribe Gaming in the World Championship final. Being a full attack, and a 9 Healer Hero Charge, it will be tricky if you're not a TH17 player, but I've broken it down into steps so that with a bit of practice you'll be able to beat the challenge. Best of luck with your 3 stars though and thank you for supporting the channel with Code Judo!

snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK
Written by Suman Kumar, Raj & DK
Screenplays by: Suman Kumar, Raj & DK, Sudhish Kamath, Nikhil Gonsalves  
Dialogues: Sumit Arora

Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma
Executive Producer: Vikesh Bhutani, Ankita Batra
Associate Director: Chesta Goswami

Director Of Photography: Jay Charola
Production Designer: Parichit Paralkar
Editor: Sumeet Kotian
Post-Production Producer: Jespal Nadar
Action Directors: Yannick Ben Haddou, Aejaz Gulab
Sound Design: Sanjay Maurya & Allwin Rego
Background Score: Ketan Sodha 
Costume Designer: Neha. R. Bajaj
Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA 

First Assistant Director: Durgesh Pratap Singh 
Additional Writing: Suhas Navarathna
Production Supervisor: Utkarsha Kohli 
Special Advisor: Bimal Parekh

A D2R Films Production

Actors:
Manoj Bajpayee

Music credits - Kohinoor by DIVINE, written by - DIVINE, iLL Wayno

Trailer Background score by Aman Pant

Official Release Date November 21, 2025 on Prime Video India

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. snippet.title: Cricket 26 - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the official trailer for Cricket 26, the official game of the Ashes. Take command of your favourite team in the all-new Management Career Mode. Experience cricket's biggest rivalry in the expanded Ashes Mode. Step up to a whole new level of control with enhanced batting mechanics. 

Cricket 26 will be released on November 20, 2025 for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.

snippet.title: Jana Nayagan ‚Äì Trailer| Thalapathy Vijay|Sanjay Dutt| Yogi Babu| Pooja Hegde|#thalapathyvijay #tvk
snippet.description:
Jana Nayagan ‚Äì Official Narrative Trailer
A story that rises from the streets, built on truth, sacrifice, and the voice of the people.

When a corrupt political empire tightens its grip on the city, one officer stands between justice and destruction.
Vetri Vel IPS (Vijay) ‚Äî a fearless cop with a past filled with scars ‚Äî steps into a war he never asked for.
Facing him is a ruthless power-driven force led by Sanjay Dutt, a man who controls fear, money, and lives.

Standing alone, surrounded by chaos, betrayals, and political violence, Vetri Vel fights not just for law‚Ä¶
But for the people who lost everything.

This narrative trailer reveals:
‚úÖ The emotional journey of a fearless officer
‚úÖ The rise of a dangerous political villain
‚úÖ A city collapsing under corruption
‚úÖ Love, pain, and sacrifice
‚úÖ Epic action, mass moments & powerful dialogues

A complete, story-focused trailer designed to give you the soul of the film ‚Äî without revealing the climax.

‚ú® This is a fan-made project created with passion for storytelling and cinema.
üî• More cinematic cuts, scenes & breakdowns coming soon! #thalapathyvijay #tvk #ungavijay #poojahegde #trailer #tranding #jananayagan #jananayaganupdate #thalaphathykechari

snippet.title: HUM BAS TERE HAIN - Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat | Harshvardhan & Sonam | B Praak, Rahul, Rish & Prince
snippet.description:
Teri Deewaniyat mein guzre din mere hain, #HumBasTereHain
‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî• Song out now

#EkDeewaneKiDEEWANIYAT Booking open: https://bookmy.show/HI_EDKD

In Cinemas Now!

Song : Hum bas tere hain 
Music : Rahul Mishra 
Lyrics : Prince Dubey 
Singer : B Praak
Music producer : The Rish

PlayDMF Team :-
Founder & CEO : Anshul Garg  
Vice President : Raghav Sharma ( Pratick Sharma)
Label Manager : Sankalp Garg
Project & Artist Manager : Gaurav Arora
Legal & Digital Manager : Ashima Chauhan
PlayDMF Team : Aansi Agrawal & Anshu Prasad
Artwork : Vicky Sandhu
Special Thanks : Virgin Music India

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria

https://www.virginmusic.com/

Lyrics :-
Chaahe ye zamana badal bhi jaaye
Aa jaaye yahan daur koi
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge
Na aayega aur koi 

Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge
Hum ye kah rahe hain
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge 

Rasta ek ho tera mera yahan 
Maangta hoon main aur kuch bhi Kahan
Tu mujhe jo mile dard mere hansenge 
Kaash mujhko tu bhi yun hi chaahta 

Haar jaaun kahin toh junoon tu bane
Zindagi bhar ka mere sukoon tu bane 

Ab meri shaamein mere savere
Honge na tere bagair koi 
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge 
Na aayega aur koi 
Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge 
Hum ye kah rahe hain 
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge

#HarshvardhanRane #SonamBajwa #DeewaniyatKiDiwali #Diwali2025.

snippet.title: Bulbul | Muhfaad | Kartavya | 2025
snippet.description:
Music/Mix/Master - Kartavya
Lyrics - Muhfaad 

Bandar chadha pahaad pe karke 
chutadh chaude
chup kyu hai baitha bol sorry behn ke!!

naach meri bulbul milega tujhe paisa
mita du teri chull mile jaise ko taisa
aaye na samajh tujhe izzat ka lehza
bewaqoof nahi dekha tere jaisa.

aadhe ganje 
adhe rapper
adhi shakti 
adhi mehnat
kaise sun lu 
kyu lu seh kar
kaun behtar
you know better

muhfaad kare muh pe blabber
rate hue sabke pattern
tu hi monseure tu hi madam
wig laga ke lagte karen

chidhta hai to chidhta reh
mai to karu daya na
kauwa kha ke goo
kis muh se bane sayana?

bat suno bhaijaan
muh pe maru paaydaan
faltu jo khaye kaan
to sareaam fir trahimam

leta kaun tujhe serious
get ready for veer ras
banda nahi tu gimmick 
Mr. idiot on periods.
chahye nahi opinion
mai 16 se nahi lenient
karu break character tera 
lo so that you can be real

ye koi beef wala nyauta nahi
tujhe bhaunkne se roka nahi
yad dilau doodh chhati ka par
hazam tujhe hoga nahi
soongh bagle aur kachhiyan
tu aur kisi jogga nahi
likhne se chutkule 
muqabla hoga nahi.

tere jaisi thuki mile
road pe baleno
mai bas dikhta hu akela
aake maarte hai teeno
mere jaise likhna hai to 
lagenge maheeno 
tujhe koi bhi na dhoondhe
agar hota bhi tu nemo

firse chadha bali 
haththe UP wale ke
tere area ke laundo
ko duty baatenge
ise sapno ki duniya se kheech ke laao
sare aate jate bulbul ko chooti katenge

apas ke mazak mat la screen pe
yahan baksha nahi kisi ko maine scene me
ye goat kya hai puchhte hai memne
bhosdi ke sote ke de dunga neend me.

snippet.title: O Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehbooba (Music Video) - Mohammed Rafi | Dharmendra Hits Songs
snippet.description:
Enjoy the evergreen romantic track ‚ÄúO Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehbooba‚Äù sung by the legendary Mohammed Rafifrom the movie Dharam Veer (1977). Featuring the dynamic Dharmendra and the stunning Zeenat Aman, this melodious song . 

#OMeriMehbooba #MohammedRafi #Dharmendra #ZeenatAman #DharamVeer #LaxmikantPyarelal #BollywoodClassics #EvergreenSongs #OldBollywoodSongs #HindiSongs #BollywoodHits #RomanticSongs 

Credits: 
Singer: Mohammed Rafi
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Dharam Veer
Starring: Dharmendra, Zeenat Aman
Director: Manmohan Desai
Producer: Subhash Desai
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 
  
O meri mehbooba mehbooba mehbooba 

tujhey jaana hai toh jaa teri marji mera kya 

par dekh jo tu ruth kar chali jayegi 

tere saath hi mere marne ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Teri chahat mera chain churaigi 

lekin tujko bhi to nind na ayegi 

main toh mar jaunga leka naam tera 

naam magar kar jaunga badnam tera 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad mein meri tujko tadapaigi 

tere jaatey hi tere aane ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Jo bhi meri is prem kahani ka 

par kya hoga teri mast jawani ka 

ashiq hoon main tere dil me raheta hoon 

apni nahin main tere dil ki kaheta hoon 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad me teri tu pachtaegi 

yeh ruth jawani ki judai main hi guzar jayegi 

O meri mehbooba

snippet.title: Matter (Official Music Video) - Sumit Parta & Panther | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Presenting new Haryanvi hip hop 2025 ‚Äì Matter by Sumit Parta & Panther

Bringing you the raw and fearless vibe of Haryana with "Matter", the latest fire track by Sumit Parta & Panther.
This song defines real street energy ‚Äî filled with power, attitude, and pride. With intense lyrics, bold delivery, and unstoppable flow, Matter is all about dominance, loyalty, and living with no compromise.

If you believe in your hustle and never back down ‚Äî this one‚Äôs for you. 

Song Credits: 
Song Title: Matter
Singer: Sumit Parta & Panther
Music: Xtacy
Lyricist/Composer: Sumit Parta & Panther

Director: Mohan BeTaab
DOP: Nishan Singh

Distribution By: EYP Consulting
Distribution & Marketing Partner: EYP Creations & Warner Music India
Digitally Managed By: Prince Pannu

Lyrics:
Gaadi Uchi Uchi Rakhe Chale Talke Sedan 
Baat Lambi Koni Khiche Khde Pair Samadhan 
Sath Khaadi Panchgami Kon Gunda Paake Shayami 
Mkha Itni Re Bdi Koni Kise Ki Dukan 

Yaari Dosti Me Sara Ghar Phuk Dewa 
Par Yaari Dosti Me Koni Roli Chalya Kre 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
 Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya  Kre 

Bair Mhare Chori Sun Dada Layi Chalre H
Gelya Chacha Tau Aale Mere Bhai Chalre H 
Kayi Sale Mere Laan Ki Sakeem Sochre H 
Anty Party Te  Krn Collab Pochre H 

Phle Karam Kand Krya Ib Bnya Hu Me  Singer 
Choro Jaata Ko  Sage Bishnoiya Ka Tinger 
Adhe Shise Khule Bhar Kade Rakhe Chora Finger
5,7 Bhai Paad Dewa Karwayi 
Konya Krke Yo Chora Kathi Toli Chalya Krya 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre 

Ye Ghoda Chalta Bhi Aur Jalta Bhi
Bas Bhaagta Bhagataa Lekin Peecha Hat-ta Nahi
Ye Ghoda Jeet Dilata Aur Karta Barbaadi
Deta Nahi Maafi Hai Karta Sardari
Aur Faadein Beech Se Gar Bane Koi Jyada Patwari

Raub Jamata Ye Gaddafi Nahi Jhukta Bhale Hi Katta Sir
Mujhe Gaddari Dikhe Minute Se Pehle Got The Vision Of Gandhari
Hoti Mahabharat Tune Buri Nazar Se Dekh Li Gar Meri Panchali
Tere Chacha Bappa Sabki Karwadu Baikunth Tayyari
Aur Sun
Kam Se Jyaada Hai Zubaan Ki Izzat
Aukat Se Jyaada Karte Iman Ki Izzat
Chadhai Se Jyaada Ache Insan Ki
Hum Bhaukal Se Zyaada Karte Ache Khandan Ki Izzat
Gunday Badmash Company Me Jaise Ye Yashraj Ki Picture
Pakke Usool, Lathi Hai Har Sanp Ki Ksimat
Naseeb Me Bheji Bhagwan Ne Pehli Ashiqui Likh Kar
Aur Duji Maut Seene Pe Goli Hath Me Pistol

Hoti Pitayi Lage Kohli Mara Kare
Judge Sab Bole Galat Karam Pe Tere Moti Dhara Lage
Khatey Bikaneri Na Goli Guli Khaya Kare
Panther Bhaiya Jaha Phonchey Og Og Nara Lage

Mkha Kaan Khol Dhyan Te Tu Baat Sun Chooti

snippet.title: Tu Cheez Badi Hai Mast Mast [4K Lyrical] | Mohra 1994 | Akshay Kumar, Raveena Tandon | Superhit Song
snippet.description:
"Tu Cheez Badi Hai Mast Mast" is a popular Bollywood song from the 1994 film Mohra. The track was sung by Udit Narayan and Kavita Krishnamurthy, with music composed by Viju Shah and lyrics penned by Anand Bakshi. The song became iconic for its catchy beat and energetic vocals, and it features the legendary performances of actors Akshay Kumar and Raveen Tondon.

snippet.title: Love Exit - Jind Universe (OFFICIAL VIDEO)
snippet.description:
The viral sensation of the year, Jind Universe, is back after High On You with his latest drop - Love Exit. In this one, Jind doesn‚Äôt just sing, he inhabits the moment. He‚Äôs that figure sitting under dappled light, half in shadow, half in glow, every verse a measured step between softness and strength. His presence is minimal in theatrics, maximum in feeling.


‚ô´
Song Tittle: Love Exit
Singer: Jind Universe
Lyrics: Jind Universe
Music/composer: Jind Universe

Video: Director Jsie

Spot: Prakashwaran Batumalai

Strategically Promoted: Hatke Media

Mitthe tere bol jivein hunde a lutere
kala till, kala dil, kaali zulfa de ghere
kyu aave na baaz teri akhan ch koi raaz jivein
jina ch kaid ni tu kitte a bthere‚Ä¶
sohniye ni yaari tethon gyi na nibhayi
bada smjhaya tenu samajh ni ayi
hun jado kru tenu tang tanhaayi
fe hovengi preshaan..

Baki jo tenu thik lage meri jaan

tere bina v thik lage eh jahaan

jinna tuttiyan da chah tenu

galti c meri jo ditti main panaah
avein kar gyi fanaah kudde teri ae adaaah menu

Roz ni milde saaf jhe dil de
saade jahe insaan,
tenu lagge tu mainu bhuljengi saukha
